item.title: My Other Camera Is
item.description:
My Other Camera Is

This site is dedicated to all things iPhone all images and video was taken with an iPhone 6+. This site was published and built on the iPhone 6+ using The Grid iOS app. The Grid has created new programming language for layout design harnessing the power of A.I. for a pragmatic design of feed-based layouts.
